data.description: **ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE! 3.8% INTEREST RATE AVAILABLE**    Discover an exceptional opportunity within the confines of the gated Eastwood at Riverside community. This standalone residence, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, enjoys a prime location offering seamless access to multiple landmarks, including Downtown Austin, the vibrant East Side, Town Lake, the airport, and East Side Gateway—an expansive mixed-use development currently underway. This location will only get better as residents may soon enjoy access to the entire city via a planned light rail line connecting Austin-Bergstrom International Airport with Downtown Austin.   This stunning residence showcases a thoughtfully designed layout, soaring ceilings that flood the space with natural light, and a luxurious primary bedroom and bathroom on the first floor.   Revel in the exquisite touches, including gorgeous honeywood flooring in the entry and kitchen, indulgent walk-in showers, bespoke fixtures, and cutting-edge smart technology.  Enjoy a hassle-free, lock-and-leave lifestyle as the HOA meticulously tends to the landscaping needs of both the front and back yards.  Location, convenience, and imagination make this property an unbeatable opportunity for homebuyers and savvy investors. Don't miss the chance to explore this exceptional gem!
